import React from 'react' import "./Logs.css" import data from "../data/sample.json" export const Logs = ({ ftype, flever, fsearch }) => { console.log(data) return (

Logs

{ data.map((log, index) => { if ((ftype === "All" || log.type === ftype) && (flever === "All" || log.level === flever) && (fsearch === "" || log.message.toLowerCase().includes(fsearch.toLowerCase()) || log.resource.toLowerCase().includes(fsearch.toLowerCase()) || log.commit.toLowerCase().includes(fsearch.toLowerCase()) || log.traceId.toLowerCase().includes(fsearch.toLowerCase()))) { return (
{log.level} {log.timestamp}

{log.message}

Resource: {log.resource} | Commit: {log.commit}
Trace Id:{log.traceId}
Trace Id:{log.traceId}
Trace Id:{log.traceId}
) } return null }) }
) }
